{"tid":878905,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股王400元】冇買騰訊冇買樓　網民愁爆錯失全世界","createTime":"2018-10-27T13:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T11:06:28.000Z","uid":122318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9c2cee85909b97617cfd9331ab60fbb6f7545b","tid":878905,"uid":122318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510887311_15e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510887311_15e3.jpg&h=b1e54e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騰訊（700）今日升穿400元，以一拆五拆細前計算，股價已升穿2,000元，以04年上市價3.7元計，騰訊已累升539.5倍，網民一篇《問君能有幾多愁，沒買騰訊沒買樓》，再度熱炒，令人再度感嘆，未置業的朋友，如果錯過騰訊，將會有幾慘。<br />\n文章聲稱，騰訊於12年剛推出微信時，市值大約4,000多億元，但目前已高達3.7萬億元。「很多人將騰訊和買樓放在一起比較，成為過去幾年最好的投資產品。」文章在8月推出時已引起共鳴，亦有很多網友認為騰訊股價已十分高，當時買入不是太明智，但事實上，騰訊股價由8月至今，由308元再升了三成，可謂高處未算高。<br />\n文章又指，當初錯過買樓的同學，覺得錯過了直升機撒錢；錯過蘋果的股民，可能感覺錯過了整個宇宙，「錯過了騰訊，你是否感覺錯過了全世界？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171117/57468971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57468971&d=vBTfQxO9OeUepJqlu6n2%2F8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=776df20c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57468971&h=5d2189d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171117/57468971</a>"},{"pid":"1dc625d1c94208da6c5452c856d8a2981b6412f0","tid":878905,"uid":122318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e9c2cee85909b97617cfd9331ab60fbb6f7545b","tid":878905,"uid":122318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510887311_15e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstati